title: Big 12 coaches pick Kansas to win conference basketball title, OU is 2nd and OSU 7th
text:
Big 12 coaches pick Kansas to win conference basketball title, OU is 2nd and OSU 7th THE ASSOCIATED PRESS   4:23 pmLast   4:23 pm   
Organizations: 
Oklahoma (553) 
OKLAHOMA CITY â€” Kansas is the choice of Big 12 coaches to win the conference basketball title with Oklahoma picked to finish second and Oklahoma State seventh. 
Kansas received nine of the 10 first place votes in the poll released Thursday. Coaches are not allowed to vote for their own team. 
Kansas and OU are followed by Iowa State, which received the other first place vote, Texas, Baylor, West Virginia, OSU, Kansas State and TCU tied for eighth, and Texas Tech.
